o was able to see behind the veil, past the phenomenal leader to a person who I am better for having known.&lt;br /&gt;And here is to Ernie Villanueva &lt;a href="http://ernievillanueva.com"&gt;http://ernievillanueva.com&lt;/a&gt; for always being inspiring.&lt;br /&gt;Also to J Douglas Edwards and the legacy he left; Tony Robbins &lt;a href="http://tonyrobbins.com"&gt;http://tonyrobbins.com&lt;/a&gt;, Zig Ziglar &lt;a href="http://zigziglar.com"&gt;http://zigziglar.com&lt;/a&gt;, Robert Kiyosaki &lt;a href="http://richdad.com"&gt;http://richdad.com&lt;/a&gt; and so many others that have inspired so many of us to follow our dreams.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;And here is to my beautiful wife Kathy &lt;a href="http://katslife.com"&gt;http://katslife.com&lt;/a&gt; for always believing in me, always listening to and wanting my advise on sales and for encouraging me to share what I know. May you continue to have all the success you deserve in Big Yellow Box by Crayola hun :)&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;And to Marjie and all my students from DOUA &lt;a href="http://doua.org"&gt;http://doua.org&lt;/a&gt; who showed me that the things I have to say about sales really do help better peoples lives.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Last but not least and all the my other mentors and dear friends I love you all!&lt;br /&gt;To all those who went before us and have made this country what it is; a true land where a person can have a dream and ambition and can achieve anything their heart desires! THANK YOU!!&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;script type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;!--

